headline: Stifel Cuts Essex Property Trust (ESS) PT to $278 After Q4 Review, Keeps Hold
summary: Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) is included among the 13 Cheapest Dividend Aristocrats to Invest in. On February 5, Stifel trimmed its price recommendation on Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) to $278 from $290.75. It reiterated a Hold rating on the stock. The adjustment followed updates to the firm’s estimates after reviewing the company’s fourth-quarter results. […]
